OL,3,CHistoric library saved by community
OL,4,Cgets funding boost for renovations
OL,6,FAn historic building in Cornwall has
OL,7,Fsecured almost #250,000 from the
OL,8,FNational Lottery Heritage Fund for
OL,9,Fmajor renovation work.
OL,11,FRedruth's Passmore Edwards building on
OL,12,FClinton Road, now named The Ladder, is
OL,13,Fa Grade II-listed former library and
OL,14,Fadjoining college.
OL,16,FWhen the building was established in
OL,17,F1895, it embodied Passmore Edwards'
OL,18,Fdedication to creating spaces that
OL,19,Ffostered social mobility.
