OL,3,CHistoric library saved by community
OL,4,Cgets funding boost for renovations
OL,6,FIt was rescued by the Redruth Former
OL,7,FLibrary CIC in 2021, after it was
OL,8,Falmost sold off for flats the previous
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FThe building's new name is inspired by
OL,12,FPassmore Edwards' quote, "If I can
OL,13,Ffund the Ladder; the people will
OL,14,Fclimb" and was chosen by the public in
OL,15,Fan online poll.
