OL,3,CHistoric library saved by community
OL,4,Cgets funding boost for renovations
OL,6,FThe Ladder will become a centre for
OL,7,Fheritage, culture, and education,
OL,8,Fproviding a community space for
OL,9,FRedruth.
OL,11,FThe project, which is jointly funded
OL,12,Fwith the Shared Prosperity Fund, will
OL,13,Finclude a cafe, nursery, rehearsal
OL,14,Fspace, community space, exhibition
OL,15,Fspace, co-working space, darkroom and
OL,16,Fartist studios.
OL,18,FThe college has already been
OL,19,Ftransformed into a nursery ` providing
OL,20,Fchildcare for an initial intake of 30
OL,21,Fchildren.
