OL,3,CHistoric library saved by community
OL,4,Cgets funding boost for renovations
OL,6,FFelix Mortimer, co-director of Redruth
OL,7,FFormer Library CIC which owns the
OL,8,Fbuilding, said: "This investment in
OL,9,Fthe beautiful 1894 building,
OL,10,Fbequeathed to the people of Redruth by
OL,11,FPassmore Edwards and purchased by the
OL,12,Fcommunity in 2021 will allow us to
OL,13,Fbuild world-class workspace, rehearsal
OL,14,Fspace and podcast studio.
OL,16,F"It also means we can roll out four
OL,17,Fprojects which respond to the heritage
OL,18,Fof the town as well as carry out four
OL,19,Fprojects researching and responding to
OL,20,Fthe heritage of the town."
